  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1349060/extras/bf326531c3f1a77068da7430c1ed1d94.webp?t=1667091081\" width=609 height=60 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1349060/extras/3b331650c1592564865fde8fb7927d39.poster.avif?t=1667091081\" width=497 height=359 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1349060/extras/3b331650c1592564865fde8fb7927d39.webm?t=1667091081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>IT STEALS is a challenging experiment in survival horror, revolving around stealthy and unpredictable monstrosities. Each game mode is an escalation of that idea, featuring a new formidable evil and unique abilities to face against it. Play by their rules, or suffer their quick wrath. They are <i>always</i> present within the walls of the maze, scheming against you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1349060/extras/ebb20727a440d7be6a2c66200e4e62fa.avif?t=1667091081\" width=481 height=525 /></span><br><br>IT STEALS does not tell you everything. In each mode you are given the tools to survive, but it's on you to learn how to use them correctly. You must infer and improvise; with each death, something is learned, and victory comes a step closer.<br><br>AROUND EVERY CORNER.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1349060/extras/bf326531c3f1a77068da7430c1ed1d94.webp?t=1667091081\" width=609 height=60 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1349060/extras/3b331650c1592564865fde8fb7927d39.poster.avif?t=1667091081\" width=497 height=359 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1349060/extras/3b331650c1592564865fde8fb7927d39.webm?t=1667091081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>IT STEALS is a challenging experiment in survival horror, revolving around stealthy and unpredictable monstrosities. Each game mode is an escalation of that idea, featuring a new formidable evil and unique abilities to face against it. Play by their rules, or suffer their quick wrath. They are <i>always</i> present within the walls of the maze, scheming against you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1349060/extras/ebb20727a440d7be6a2c66200e4e62fa.avif?t=1667091081\" width=481 height=525 /></span><br><br>IT STEALS does not tell you everything. In each mode you are given the tools to survive, but it's on you to learn how to use them correctly. You must infer and improvise; with each death, something is learned, and victory comes a step closer.<br><br>AROUND EVERY CORNER.",
